<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，龙卷风小组在多诺万树屋碰了面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以在墓地里找到最古老的墓碑。”劳拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我们在哪里能找到最年长的人呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许在柳树溪养老院能找到。”乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很多老人住在那里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以在图书馆里找到社区活动日历。”卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我们怎样才能找到一条小镇法律呢？”乔伊问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她低头看了看着清单，皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们只有不到两周的时间来找到这些东西了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能帮忙！”曼尼说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，你不能。”卡洛斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是个小孩子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他会数数，对吧？”乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得数主要街道上的停车标志、邮箱和路灯。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能数到一百！”曼尼说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“足够好了。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时， 一阵灰色的烟雾飘过了树屋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉咳嗽起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡洛斯闻了闻空气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我闻到了烟味。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙卷风小组从树屋的窗户向外望去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿，爷爷！”乔伊喊道，“您在干什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷抬头看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，嘿，孩子们。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在烧一些杂草。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用一根棍子戳火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一片燃烧的叶子飘起来，落到了干草里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火苗突然窜了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃。”爷爷说，用他的靴子踩灭了火苗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那边还有一个。”卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷又踩灭了另一个火苗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那边还有一个。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷又踩灭了火苗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，到处都是小火苗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷惊慌失措地边跑边跺脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃哦。”曼尼说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们急忙跑下树屋的楼梯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去门廊后面把桶拿过来！”爷爷大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙卷风小组出发了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但当他们跑回山上时，火已经燃烧起来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>烟飘向天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷抓起水桶，到池塘里装水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把水泼在火上，但火还在继续燃烧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们听到了警笛声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“消防车！”卡洛斯喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>消防队长的卡车在前面，消防车紧跟在后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194681</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警笛声不停地响着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>车子行驶在车道上，穿过了田地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三名消防队员跳了下来，解开了消防水龙带。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“后退！”消防队长朝爷爷和孩子们大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水从水管里喷出来，喷到了火上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，火就灭了，草地上留下了一个潮湿的黑圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是怎么回事？”消防队长问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她叫丽塔·卡尔森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她当了15年柳树溪消防员。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊。”爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只是在烧一些杂草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，火蔓延得到处都是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当孩子们拿着水桶来到这里......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡尔森队长打断了爷爷的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以，您是没有为控制火势事先做好准备，是吗？”她问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有。”爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>消防队长皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多诺万先生，我可以看看您的燃烧许可证吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“燃烧许可证？”爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡尔森队长叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多诺万先生，柳树溪的《燃烧法》要求您在烧火前获得燃烧许可证。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>您违反了法律。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶！”乔伊大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都盯着乔伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这正是我们要找的！”她解释道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“寻宝游戏要找的法律！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>您有《燃烧法》副本吗，卡尔森队长？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！我们还需要一份消防安全提示清单。”劳拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没问题。”卡尔森队长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这两样东西就在我的卡车里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有，多诺万先生，我得给您开张罚款单。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，龙卷风小组欢呼了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>消防车正要离开时，凯蒂骑着自行车沿着黑莓路飞驰而来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蚯蚓小组来了！”卡洛斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别告诉她我们找到了什么！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>339696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙卷风小组大笑，在他们的清单上打了两个勾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>